ActUnited Nations Act
Special Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Implementing the United Nations Resolutions on Libya
PrecisRegulations Amending the REGULATIONS IMPLEMENTING THE UNITED NATIONS RESOLUTIONS ON LIBYA in order to bring Canada in line with its international legal obligations created by measures taken by the United Nations Security Council (UNSC) under chapter VII of the United Nations Charter, namely the decisions taken by the UNSC in Resolutions 2146 (2014), 2174 (2014) and 2362 (2017).
